Package: pkgnews
Type: Package
Title: Access Package NEWS files
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Imanuel Costigan <i.costigan@me.com>
Maintainer: Imanuel Costigan <i.costigan@me.com>
Description: Getting to read NEWS files in markdwon format can be tedious 
  from within an R session. This package provides an interface to view all types 
  of local NEWS files as well as being able to access release notes on Github 
  hosted packages.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports: utils,
    markdown,
    desc
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
